<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجِبُ غَسْلُ يَدَيِ القَائِمِ مِنْ نَوْمِ اللَّيْلِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
